Title: Jonathon Dixon: Why I joined Cloudflare
Description: I’m excited to announce that on March 1st, I joined Cloudflare as Vice President and GM, Asia Pacific (including Japan and Greater China) to help build and expand Cloudflare’s growing customer and partner base and presence in the region.

Title: Cycling is ten times more important than electric cars for reaching net-zero cities
Description: Active travel can help tackle the climate crisis earlier than electric vehicles – even if you swap the car for a bike for just one trip a day.

Title: WTF are these security chips?
Description:
There seem to be a few interesting trends in “security via hardware” these days. 
The first trend is root-of-trust chips. Integrated TPM-like chips that are like crypto Swiss Army knives as they offer many functionalities out of the box. They resemble discrete TPMs but are instead integrated directly into the main processor. This makes these newer chips faster, and also more resistant to physical  ...

Title: Cancer Diagnoses Jump at 65 Years When Medicare Kicks In
Description: An abrupt jump in cancer diagnoses at the age of 65 in the US suggests that people are not seeking medical care until they are eligible for Medicare health insurance.
